CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `videoWatchSessions` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL,
  `videoId` int NOT NULL,
  `userId` int NOT NULL,
  `startedAt` datetime NOT NULL,
  `endedAt` datetime,
  `watchedSeconds` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,
  `startPosition` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,
  `endPosition` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,
  `deviceType` varchar(50),
  `completedInSession` boolean NOT NULL DEFAULT false,
  `createdAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  CONSTRAINT `videoWatchSessions_id` PRIMARY KEY(`id`)
);
